data.title: Spring 2024 Dean’s List Honorees Announced
data.text:
1,629 students receive Dean’s List recognition for the Spring 2024 semester

The following 1,629 Monroe Community College students were named to the dean’s list for the Spring 2024 semester. Dean’s list honorees are full- and part-time students who have earned a 3.5 GPA or higher. Names are listed alphabetically by last name.
